%% --- Diagrama 3: Fluxo de dados pelo portal (jornada diária) ---

sequenceDiagram
    actor Gestor as Gestor / Analista
    participant Portal as Portal Web
    participant BFF as API BFF
    participant S3 as S3 Data Lake
    participant SFN as Step Functions
    participant Glue as Glue Jobs
    participant Lam as Lambda D-1/D-2/D-3
    participant Ath as Athena

    Note over Gestor,S3: Manhã · consumir insights de ontem (D-1)

    Gestor->>Portal: Abre dashboard D-1 (dt=2022-01-01)
    Portal->>BFF: GET /insights/d1?dt=...
    BFF->>S3: Lê enriquecido/dt= ou relatorios/D1/
    BFF-->>Portal: Ranking + insight automático
    Portal-->>Gestor: Tabela interativa + botão Excel

    Note over Gestor,Glue: TI · nova carga ou reprocessamento

    Gestor->>Portal: Upload retail_store_inventory.csv
    Portal->>BFF: POST /insumos/upload
    BFF->>S3: Grava insumo/ + valida schema
    BFF-->>Portal: OK · 15 colunas · N linhas

    Gestor->>Portal: Processar dt=2022-01-02
    Portal->>BFF: POST /pipeline/processar-dia
    BFF->>SFN: StartExecution { dt }
    SFN->>Glue: carregar_origem_dia
    Glue->>S3: origem/dt=2022-01-02/
    SFN->>Glue: enriquecer_dia
    Glue->>S3: enriquecido/dt=2022-01-02/
    SFN->>Lam: gerar D-1, D-2, D-3
    Lam->>S3: relatorios/D1|D2|D3/
    BFF-->>Portal: Execução SUCCEEDED
    Portal-->>Gestor: Insights disponíveis

    Note over Gestor,Ath: Analista · validação ad hoc

    Gestor->>Portal: SQL sobre enriquecido
    Portal->>BFF: POST /athena/query
    BFF->>Ath: SELECT ... WHERE dt=...
    Ath-->>Portal: Resultado tabular

